skdetail:

Invocation Name: guess the celeb
des:
It wouldn't be too surprising to know everything about your favorite celebrity, but what about those who have taken over the new lately. Think you know enough to be able to tell the difference between Justin Bieber and Shawn Mendes based from just one paragraph? Test your luck and your knowledge with these big celebs and see how many of them you actually get right.

Play an interesting game of quiz with Alexa. While playing the quiz, you can say "Alexa, next" to move to the next question. At any point, you can say "Alexa, stop" to exit the quiz.
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
